SMALL-BASKET*¶

*given data is about sales ,transactions and locations of "SMALL BASKET"¶

*SMALL BASKET is a "grocery retail online store" it is in the market from 2011.¶

* generally retail market is of 2 types "RETAIL" & "GROCERY-RETAIL"¶

* retail market is all about selling goods like clothing¶

* grocery-retail is all about food and house-hold suppies (mainly vegetables and fruits).¶
